%% Diagram: Supply Chain Attestation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant CI as CI runner
  participant OIDC as CI OIDC issuer
  participant Fulcio
  participant Rekor
  participant Reg as OCI registry
  participant Adm as Admission controller
  CI->>OIDC: Request workflow id token
  OIDC-->>CI: Signed JWT (workflow identity)
  CI->>Fulcio: Exchange JWT for short-lived cert
  Fulcio-->>CI: X.509 cert bound to identity
  CI->>CI: Build image, compute digest
  CI->>CI: Generate SLSA provenance and SBOM
  CI->>Rekor: Log signature and attestation
  Rekor-->>CI: Inclusion proof
  CI->>Reg: Push image + signature + in-toto attestations
  Note over Reg: Image addressed by digest, not tag
  Adm->>Reg: Pull image and attestations at deploy
  Adm->>Adm: cosign verify (identity + issuer + predicate)
  Adm-->>Reg: Admit only if policy passes
